== Advisory committee ==

While the Berkeley Forum is a student-run organization, it is supported by a faculty advisory committee, which consists of the following professors:<ref>{{cite web|url=http://forum.berkeley.edu/advisory |title=Advisory Committee |publisher= The Berkeley Forum |accessdate=May 21, 2014}}</ref>
*[http://www.alexandercoward.com/ Alexander Coward]
*[http://history.berkeley.edu/people/brian-delay Brian Delay]
*[[Christopher Edley, Jr.|Christopher Edley]]
*[http://gspp.berkeley.edu/directories/faculty/john-ellwood John Ellwood]
*[[Alexei Filippenko]]
*[[Paul Pierson]]
*[[Robert Reich]]

